Cannot connect to iPhones or iPads.POWER SUPPLY ON/COMM OFF is selected for USB POWER SUPPLY/COMM SETTING. Select POWER SUPPLY OFF/COMM ON when the camera is connected via a Lightning connection to a device that do not supply power (□□ 268).
Cannot connect to smartphone.Confirm that the camera is correctly connected: The procedure for connecting the camera varies with the type of connec- tor with which the smartphone is equipped (□□ 250).
